urns<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>We do not provide for any return and\/or refund of our product unless it was incorrectly delivered or its packaging was damaged during transit. Customers are advised to inspect the general condition of the products immediately upon receipt of the delivery. No claims shall be entertained once the delivery order has been accepted by customers.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h3><strong>PAYMENT<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>DurianBB Malaysia current only accepts payment via iPay88. IPay88 is a payment method for online purchases that allows users to make payments via bank transfer or debit\/credit card.<\/p>\n<p>IPay88 offers a fast, safe and easy method of payment without disclosing your credit card or other financial information to the merchant.<\/p>\n<p>You can also make payment via PayPal if you have balance in your account. To pay for an order in MYR currency, please ensure that your PayPal balances are in MYR currency.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>PLACING AN ORDER 1.\u00a0How To Order Register by creating an account, or Log in as existing member. Select the desired item, indicate the quantity and click on the \u201cAdd to Cart\u201d button Enter the promotion code, if any, into the field provided and click \u201cApply Code\u201d Click on the \u201cShopping Cart\u201d link to review or &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/durianbb.com.my\/order-payment\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Order &#038; Payment<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"jetpack_post_was_ever_published":false,"_starter_page_template":"","_wpcom_template_layout_category":[],"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-539","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/P9XqD0-8H","jetpack_likes_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/durianb